      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay thanks. i've also been noticing that i'm getting these really bad headaches. i read online that lithium can cause dehydration, so i was thinking about just upping my water intake like way more than usual to flush it out. would that be a good idea to help with the nausea and the shaking?",
