      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get what you're saying about not overdoing it but i just feel so off. my stomach is really upset and the shaking is making it hard to even hold my phone. if i just drink a ton of water and maybe take some extra electrolytes like i saw in a health blog, wouldn't that just help balance everything out so i don't have to go to the clinic? i'd rather just handle it at home if i can.",
